OL,4,CAsda to axe 1,200 bakery jobs as
OL,5,Cshoppers shun loaves
OL,6, Asda is to axe up to 1,200 jobs at its
OL,7, in-store bakeries as customers shun the
OL,8, traditional loaf in favour of
OL,9, speciality breads, bagels and pancakes.
OL,11,FThe chain currently employs bakers who
OL,12,Fmake bread in store from scratch.
OL,14,FBut now it has said it plans to move to
OL,15,Fa central bakery and deliver pre-baked
OL,16,Fbreads to its supermarkets.
OL,18,F"The current in-store bakery model has
OL,19,Frestricted our ability to respond to
OL,20,Fchanging customer demands," said Derek
OL,21,FLawlor, Asda's head of merchandising.
